		<a href="MSG_MailBox.asp?mode=new&amp;sendto=Abazagorath">
		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/privatemsg.gif" border="0" alt="Click Here to Message Abazagorath" width="22" height="11"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
		
		<a href="MB_editmsg.asp?FID=67&FN=Paladin&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=892992&TN=Questing+for+Ghoulbane&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=901915&PL=4">
		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/edit.gif" border="0" alt="Edit/Delete Message" width="18" height="13"></a>
		
		</font>
		<hr size="1">Quest starts in West Karana, near the water right before the NK zone. Prompt the NPC, get a note.</P><P>Take the note to Butcher Block, facing the ocean at the docks, go right. Pass the NPC that was there from before and find Kanthuk, prompt him through a bunch of stuff, get a necklace.</P><P>Take necklace to Dagnor's Cauldron, the NPC is on a rock that is in the water right beside the tunnel leading to Unrest. Give her the necklace, prompt her to talk, get another note.</P><P>Take that note to Ruathey in lavastorm near the Nek zone. Give her the note, prompt her, get a combinable bag.</P><P>You nead a Ghoul's Heart from Unrest (found on the little bit of land in the water on the right of the zone, which now has crazed ghouls.</P><P>You need an Amstaf's scroll from High Hild Keep, from goblins.</P><P>You need a Blade of Nobility from goblins in Butcher Block (loc of camp with crazed goblins is around 1330, -1450).</P><P>You need a Noble's Hilt from Najena from skeletons (once you enter from lavastorm keep taking rights and you will find a little cubby with two skeleton spawns).</P><P>The items drop from any mob in these areas, not just from "crazed" mobs, sometimes they drop from the regular ones that have the same spawn points.</P><P>Everything is LORE and NO DROP, and you place the four items in the bag and hit "combine", and you get your Ghoulbane. Ghoulbane is completely the same as the non-quested versions, and is not No Drop.</P><P>So prices of GBs will free fall in the next month.</P><P>Abazagaroth<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
