		<hr size="1">The hilt comes off, "a skeleton" there are 3 in Nejena.  They are about lv 28, respawn about every 15 min and I got the hilt on my 5th kill.</P><P>The Blade comes off of, "Crazed Goblin" or "a Goblin" in BBM. They range from about lv 30-32, not sure on respawn time, and I got my blade on the 3rd kill.</P><P>The scroll I got off of a Goblin Thief in HHK, am told there are also crazed MOBs there too.  The thief was around lv 20, and went down waaaay too easy. Got the scroll on the first kill.</P><P>The heart drops off of any ghoul from the island in back of Unrest or any Crazed Ghoul, got mine first kill again.  </P><P>Hope this helps.</P><P><i>Sularus GloryBringer<BR>Knight of Mithaniel Marr & Bringer of his Glory on The Nameless<BR>Leader of <a target=_blank href=http://www.geocities.com/derjohns/Veratae1.html>Veratae's Blade</a><BR>Bane of Evil & Protector of those who walk in the Light</i></P><P><marquee direction=left><font color=yellow size=4><b><i>Sularus GloryBringer</marquee></f></b></i></P><P><marquee direction=right><b><font color=white>Stand Tall</marquee></b></font><BR><marquee direction=left><b><font color=blue>Live with Honor</marquee></b></font><BR><marquee direction=right><b><font color=gold>and Walk in the Light</marquee></b></font><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
