d there.... sorry. I'm just tired from staying up till 3am in the morning =)</P><P>I LOVE my ghoulbane and will wield it with the respect that it deserved.</P><P>(please don't call me a hypocrit because I am 13th level and own one,  I quested for it, and feel I earned it)  <br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
